Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>IHOYA NIUNDU WA CIANA</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Yesu, niwe Mwana wa Ithe mwende-ma, kuuma mindi na </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mindi. Niwonanirie wendo waku kuri ciana na gucihimbiria, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>guciigirira moko na gucirathima. Nitugugucokeria </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngatho niundu wa kiheo kia ciana, na nitugukuhoya </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uciikurukirie wega waku na kirathimo giaku. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Cihotithie gugutukia igikura, na cikimenyage uri ho Eukaristia-ini. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Cirokwenda kuruga maundu mothe na cieheania gutungatira </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uthamaki wa Ngai na ngoro yothe. Na njira ya utethio waku, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aciari na areri marotuika igerekanio njega cia witikia, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mithiire miega. Mahe hinya, uugi na ucamba </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa kuumiriria na gutooria mooritu ma ureri. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee utuuraga na wathanaga mindi na mindi. Ni gutuike uguo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
