Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA ZA ASUBUHI</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa jina Baba na Mwana na la Roho Mtakatifu</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BABA YETU</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baba yetu uliye mbinguni, jina lako litukuzwe, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ufalme wako ufike. Utakalo lifanyike. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utupe leo mkate wetu 
wa kila siku. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utusamehe makosa yetu kama tunavyo wasamehe </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na sisi waliotukosea.
Usititie katika kishawishi </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lakini utopoe maovuni. Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALAMU MARIA</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salamu Maria, umejaa neema. Bwana yu nawe</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umebarikiwa kuliko wanawake wote </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Yesu Mzao wa tumbo lako amebarikiwa</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maria Mtakatifu Mama wa Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utuombee sisi wakosefu na saa ya kufa kwetu. Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ATUKUZWE BABA</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atukuzwe Baba na Mwana na Roho Mtakatifu </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kama mwanzo na sasa na siku zote. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>NASADIKI</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Mungu, Baba yetu Mwenyezi	</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muumba mbingu pia dunia. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nasadiki kwa Yesu Kristu Mwanaye wa pekee Bwana wetu; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>alietungwa kwa uwezo wa Roho Mtakatifu		
akazaliwa na Bikira Maria, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akateswa kwa mamlaka ya Ponsyo Pilato</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akasulibiwa, akafa, akazikwa; akashukia kuzimu. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku ya tatu akafufuka katika ; akapaa wafu mbinguni; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amekaa kuume kwa Mungu Baba Mwenyezi; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>toka huko atakuja kuwahukumu wazima na wafu; </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nasadiki kwa Roho Mtakatifu, Kanisa takatifu katoliki, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ushirika wa watakatifu, maondoleo ya dhambi, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ufufuko wa miili na uzima wa milele, Amina</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALAMU MALKIA</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salamu Malkia, Mama Mwenye huruma; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uzima, tulizo na matumaini yetu, salamu</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunakusihi ugenini hapa, sisi wana wa Eva.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunakulilia tukilalamika na kuhuzunika bondeni</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>huku kwenye machozi. Haya basi, Mwombezi wetu, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utuangalie kwa macho yako yenye huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na mwisho wa ugeni huu, utuonyeshe Yesu , </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mzao mbarikiwa wa tumbo lako. Ee mpole, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ee mwema, ee mpendelevu, Bikira Maria</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA KWA MALAIKA MLINZI</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Malaika Mlinzi wangu, unilinde katika hatari zote za roho na mwili</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA YA IMANI</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wangu, nasadiki maneno yote linalosadiki </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kufundisha Kanisa katoliki la Roma: </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwani wewe ndiwe ulifumbulia hayo, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwani hudanganyiki wala hudanganyi. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA YA MATUMAINI</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wangu natumaini nitapewa  </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa njia ya Yesu Kristu, neema zako duniani </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na utukufu mbinguni, kwani ndiwe uliyeagana </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hayo nasi, nawe mwamini. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA YA MAPENDO</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wangu, nakupenda zaidi ya chochote; </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwani ndiwe mwema, ndiwe mwenye kupendeza. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nampenda na jirani yangu kama nafsi yangu, kwa ajili yako. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA YA KUTUBU</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wangu, nimetubu sana dhambi zangu, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwani ndiwe mwema, ndiwe mwenye kupendeza, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wachukuzwa na dhambi zangu. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi sitaki kukosa tena, nitafanya kitubio, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naomba neema yako nipate kurudi. Amina</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>MALKIA WA BWANA</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makia wa Bwana alimpasha habari Maria. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naye akapata miimba kwa uwezo wa Roho Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salamu Maria .......</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndimi mtumishi wa Bwana, nitendewe ulivyonena.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salamu Maria ......</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Mungu akatwaa mwili. Akakaa kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Salamu Maria .......</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utuombee Mzazi mtakatifu wa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tujaliwe ahadi za Kristu. Tuombe</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunakuomba Ee Bwana, utie neema yako mioyoni mwetu, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ili sisi tuliojua kwa maelezo ya malaika kwamba Mwanao </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amejifanya mtu kwa mateso na msalaba wake, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tufikishwe kwenye utukufu na ufufuko.</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunaomba hayo kwa njia ya Kristu Bwana wetu. Amina
			</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"},BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
